        "verse_indices": [
          69
        ],
        "category": "Deities_and_Oaths",
        "entity_or_term": "اللَهُ",
        "notes": "The statement 'qad kafānī Allāhu' (God has sufficed me) refers to God as a protective and sufficient divine entity, consistent with pre-Islamic beliefs in a supreme deity."
      },
      {
