        "category": "Cosmological_Concepts",
        "entity_or_term": "عاداً",
        "notes": "The mention of 'ʿĀd' refers to an ancient, powerful tribe whose destruction is a common theme in pre-Islamic Arabian lore, reflecting a cosmological understanding of divine judgment and the fate of nations."
      },
